{"tid":2046172,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求教，到底點用一通個system","createTime":"2020-06-01T08:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T11:11:54.000Z","uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62db60f77550bd6085eff7add1334adcb7f76705","tid":2046172,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"我係今年先開始用一通，之前用富逃牛牛<br />\n我係一通都叫玩個超過100張權/期<br />\n但係到上次就唔小心搞錯左 （夜）（晚）<br />\n所以個system當我同時有1張好倉 1張淡倉<br />\n<br />\n今晚又出現左一通受害者 大家入黎恥笑佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2042060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2042060</a><br />\n<br />\n但係頭先又出現類似情況了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFxtYVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFxtYVB.png&h=1bb43fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係張細恒232C 我沽出時間係今日2pm 但係佢又括住左（夜）<br />\n我驚又好似上次咁，想平倉但係當我係買入開倉 結果變左1好1淡<br />\n又扣住左按金，夜晚冇得玩<br />\n<br />\n如果我想今晚平左呢張野 可以點做？"},{"pid":"cfc0d56a78c2696bf16545d07019b2abfa89f602","tid":2046172,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"開頭用都冇問題，最近可能我一時用電腦，一時用手機<br />\n所以就搞到上次咁"},{"pid":"0704de11c9fc3ceed3c11ce6c0457fd6d14f397a","tid":2046172,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"上次係開倉用電腦 平倉用左手機落order平倉<br />\n所以可能當左我係【買入開倉】，結果就MHI+1 MHI-1<br />\n<br />\n上次係futures 今次係options 唔知又會唔會有呢個問題？"},{"pid":"d8f104fa07a8a6addc21022daf35d6308fb7b18d","tid":2046172,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"如果怕錯 最好係 持倉個個頁面 做平倉"},{"pid":"91da8a0b92056eee646e3af4e5473d1ef1aba746","tid":2046172,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee58f6a6f7675674d27d6715a5c98a5da6f8cea3","tid":2046172,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"打去cs問好過"}]}